<mvt:item name="html_profile" />
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><base href="&mvte:global:basehref;"><title>Sinister Diesel Sponsorship Application</title><meta name="description" content="Apply to the Sinister Diesel sponsorship program. Share your truck build, content channels and audience information with our team."><mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if><mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" /></head>
<body class="single-column sd2-sponsor-page"><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />
<main class="sd2-cp sd2-sponsor">
	<section class="sd2-cp__hero" aria-labelledby="sd2-sponsor-title"><div class="sd2-cp__hero-media" aria-hidden="true"><img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%201.png" alt="" fetchpriority="high"></div><div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-cp__hero-grid"><div><p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Community / Sponsorship program</p><h1 id="sd2-sponsor-title">Show us<br>your build.</h1><p class="sd2-cp__lede">Tell us about your truck, your content and the audience you serve. Our team reviews each application for brand and program fit.</p><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="#application">Start application</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="about-us-19356.html">About Sinister Diesel</a></div></div><aside class="sd2-cp__hero-console"><span class="sd2-cp__console-kicker">Application profile</span><strong>Truck.<br>Content. Reach.</strong><div class="sd2-cp__console-data"><span>Build details</span><span>Social channels</span><span>Team review</span></div></aside></div></section>
	<div class="sd2-cp__signal"><div><span>01</span><strong>Describe the truck</strong></div><div><span>02</span><strong>Share active channels</strong></div><div><span>03</span><strong>Submit for review</strong></div></div>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section" id="application" aria-labelledby="sd2-sponsor-form-title"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div class="sd2-cp__section-head"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Sponsorship application</p><h2 id="sd2-sponsor-form-title">Give the team a clear view of your build.</h2></div><p>Complete the required information accurately. Submission does not guarantee acceptance or a specific sponsorship arrangement.</p></div><div class="sd2-sponsor__form"><mvt:item name="readytheme" param="contentsection( 'sponsor_app' )" /></div></div></section>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section sd2-cp__section--dark" aria-labelledby="sd2-sponsor-review"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div class="sd2-cp__section-head"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">What helps an application</p><h2 id="sd2-sponsor-review">Specific beats impressive-sounding.</h2></div><p>Clear details help our team understand the vehicle, the work already completed and how your content connects with diesel owners.</p></div><div class="sd2-cp__feature-grid"><article><span>01 / Vehicle</span><h3>Complete build</h3><p>Include year, engine, current modifications and the purpose of the truck.</p></article><article><span>02 / Content</span><h3>Active channels</h3><p>Share the accounts where you consistently publish relevant work.</p></article><article><span>03 / Audience</span><h3>Real engagement</h3><p>Explain who follows the build and what information they value.</p></article><article><span>04 / Fit</span><h3>Brand alignment</h3><p>Show how your approach supports responsible, useful diesel content.</p></article></div></div></section>
</main><mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" /></body></html>
